Package: shinyAssistantUI
Title: AI Assistant Chat UI for Shiny
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Kaiping", "Yang", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "1260146556@qq.com")
Description: Wraps the '@assistant-ui/react' JavaScript library as a Shiny
    htmlwidget, providing a full-featured AI chat UI with streaming output,
    slash command menu, file attachments, and tool call display.
    Backend-agnostic: works with ClaudeAgentSDK, ellmer, or any R-based
    AI backend.
